@193 = ~While seen with less frequency than some other Mage Robes, those of Electrical Resistance can hardly be considered a rarity. Some are worn by paranoiacs seeking protection from a ragged mountain storm but many more are worn by mages seeking to protect themselves from the intrigues of others of their kind.

