@196 = ~Traveler's Robe~
@197 = ~This mage robe has been designed for use by rambling, itinerant mages that travel from town to town. Its enchantments not only provide protection from the bandit's arrows but also allow the wearer to move with extraordinary speed without effort. As with other robes of its kind, the Traveler's Robe can only be worn by mages.

STATISTICS:

