@198 = ~Adventurer's Robe~
@199 = ~Former Royal Magician Vangerdahast to King Azoun IV of Cormyr was once an accomplished adventurer of high fame. One reason he became popular in wizardly circles was his creation of the Adventurer's Robe. Mages have always struggled with the limitations placed on them by the ability to cast arcane magics. These robes give the mage an edge in surviving encounters with melee fighters by being able to absorb some damage from hits.

STATISTICS:

Equipped Abilities:
 Physical Damage Resistance: +10% bonus

Weight: 4
Usable By:
